        <title><![CDATA[その日の後刻に]]></title>
        <content:encoded><![CDATA[<a href="https://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/ASIN/B089NJ6H1J/hail2unet-22"><img alt="その日の後刻に" height="500" loading="lazy" src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/P/B089NJ6H1J.jpg" width="345"></a>]]></content:encoded>
